The '''Continuum Void''' was a [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] located in the city of [[Xakrea]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Darkknell/Legends|Darkknell]] and one of the few places in the city that stocked [[Gralish liqueur]].

It was here that [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]] was supposed to meet an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] defector who was willing to share information on the first [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] for the right price. Unfortunately for Bel Iblis, the [[Datacard/Legends|datapack]] with the information was lifted by master thief [[Moranda Savich]] before the deal could be done. It was also pegged by Inspector [[Hal Horn]] of [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] as a likely place for Savich to hang out; he would later visit the tapcafe in search of the woman.

